      <title>莫桑比克警告不要在计票过程中煽动他人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/mozambique-warns-against-incitement-as-vote-counting-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克总检察长警告称，不要在 10 月 9 日举行的选举当局公布结果之前煽动暴力或过早宣布胜利，计票工作于周一继续进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/mozambique-warns-against-incitement-as-vote-counting-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 18:32:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利计划通过税率和减税措施向企业减税 40 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/italy-targets-4-billion-from-firms-via-tax-rates-deductions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据了解意大利预算计划的人士透露，意大利政府计划通过调整部分税收门槛和取消某些税收减免，向企业减免 40 亿欧元（合 44 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/italy-targets-4-billion-from-firms-via-tax-rates-deductions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 18:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Eskom 呼吁提高 36% 电价，南非政治因素被归咎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/eskom-s-call-for-36-price-hike-blamed-on-south-african-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国有电力公司表示，由于政府无力控制拖欠电费的市政当局，且监管机构在审核先前提高电价的申请时出现错误，该公司不得不要求将电价提高 36%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/eskom-s-call-for-36-price-hike-blamed-on-south-african-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 18:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默试图在预算出台前重拾“财富创造者”的头衔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/starmer-tries-to-reclaim-wealth-creator-mantle-before-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 在伦敦举行的盛大投资峰会上宣称，增长和创造财富是其政府的基石，试图结束其执政头三个月的艰难时期。在这三个月里，斯塔默对公共财政状况发表的负面言论给经济情绪造成了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/starmer-tries-to-reclaim-wealth-creator-mantle-before-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 18:07:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃里克·霍尔德预测哈里斯将比特朗普多获得 500 万张选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/holder-predicts-harris-will-get-5-million-more-votes-than-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前司法部长埃里克·霍尔德表示，他预计副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将在普选中以 500 万张选票击败唐纳德·特朗普，尽管他预测由于美国选举团制度，竞争将会非常激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/holder-predicts-harris-will-get-5-million-more-votes-than-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 16:43:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党放弃英国国家银行与绿色投资改革的合并计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/labour-scraps-state-bank-merger-in-green-investment-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新工党政府已将计划拨给新国家财富基金的纳税人资金削减了五分之一，并取消了两家国家投资机构之间的合并提议，因为其雄心壮志与该国严峻的财政现实相冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/labour-scraps-state-bank-merger-in-green-investment-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 15:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大与印度因警方指控莫迪外交官而爆发争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/india-says-canada-wants-to-question-top-diplomat-in-sikh-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大和印度互相驱逐对方最高级特使，两国关系裂痕急剧扩大，而加拿大警方则全面指控印度外交官和特工涉嫌“不断升级”的谋杀和勒索事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/india-says-canada-wants-to-question-top-diplomat-in-sikh-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 10:13:26 GMT</pubDate>
